# Cinematic Frame Admin – Backend Implementation Plan

Node.js + Express.js + MySQL backend running on **port 5000**, powering every page of the admin panel.

---

## Admin Panel → Backend Mapping

| Admin Page | Data Needed | DB Table |
|---|---|---|
| **Dashboard** | Total inquiries, revenue, active projects, recent quotations | Aggregates from `quotations`, `clients` |
| **Quotations** | Lead list, status update, details panel | `quotations` |
| **Portfolio** | Albums grid, categories, featured toggle, image upload | `portfolios` |
| **Services** | Services list, packages, add/edit/delete | `services` |
| **Clients** | Client CRM, search, project count, total spent | `clients` |
| **Testimonials** | Reviews list, approve/reject | `testimonials` |
| **Analytics** | Revenue chart data, monthly totals | Aggregates from `quotations` |
| **Settings** | Admin profile, password change | `users` |

---

