---

### [NEW] `.env`
```
PORT=5000
DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=         ← fill your XAMPP MySQL password
DB_NAME=pixcel_db
JWT_SECRET=cinematic_secret_2026
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:8080
```

### [NEW] `server.js`
- Express app setup
- CORS with `FRONTEND_URL` origin
- Helmet, Morgan loggers
- Static `/uploads` folder served
- All route modules mounted under `/api`
- Global error handler

