### Database Models

#### [NEW] `User.js`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | INTEGER PK | Auto increment |
| username | VARCHAR | |
| email | VARCHAR | Unique |
| password | VARCHAR | bcrypt hashed |
| role | ENUM | `admin`, `manager` |

#### [NEW] `Quotation.js`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | INTEGER PK | |
| name | VARCHAR | Client name |
| email | VARCHAR | |
| phone | VARCHAR | |
| city | VARCHAR | |
| eventType | VARCHAR | Wedding, Corporate… |
| eventDate | DATE | |
| venue | VARCHAR | |
| guestCount | VARCHAR | |
| servicesRequested | JSON | Array of strings |
| budget | VARCHAR | |
| requirements | TEXT | |
| status | ENUM | `New`, `Contacted`, `Booked`, `Closed` |

#### [NEW] `Portfolio.js`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | INTEGER PK | |
| title | VARCHAR | Album name |
| category | ENUM | Wedding, Pre-Wedding, Corporate, Portraits, Events |
| coverImage | VARCHAR | File path |
| images | JSON | Array of file paths |
| clientName | VARCHAR | |
| eventDate | DATE | |
| featured | BOOLEAN | Default false |
| photoCount | INTEGER | |

#### [NEW] `Service.js`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | INTEGER PK | |
| name | VARCHAR | |
| description | TEXT | |
| icon | VARCHAR | lucide icon name |
| price | DECIMAL | |
| duration | VARCHAR | e.g. "8-10 hrs" |
| popular | BOOLEAN | |
| features | JSON | Array of strings (for packages) |
| packageName | VARCHAR | Silver / Gold / Platinum / null |

#### [NEW] `Client.js`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | INTEGER PK | |
| name | VARCHAR | |
| email | VARCHAR | Unique |
| phone | VARCHAR | |
| projectCount | INTEGER | Default 0 |
| totalSpent | DECIMAL | Default 0 |
| status | ENUM | `Active`, `Inactive` |

#### [NEW] `Testimonial.js`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | INTEGER PK | |
| name | VARCHAR | |
| event | VARCHAR | |
| rating | INTEGER | 1-5 |
| text | TEXT | |
| approved | BOOLEAN | Default false |

