### API Endpoints

#### Auth
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Public | Login, returns JWT |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | 🔒 Admin | Get own profile |
| PATCH | `/api/auth/change-password` | 🔒 Admin | Change password |

#### Dashboard
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/dashboard/stats` | 🔒 Admin | Total inquiries, active projects, revenue, completed |
| GET | `/api/dashboard/revenue-chart` | 🔒 Admin | Monthly revenue for chart |

#### Quotations
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/quotations` | Public | Submit from website form |
| GET | `/api/quotations` | 🔒 Admin | All leads with filter |
| GET | `/api/quotations/:id` | 🔒 Admin | Single lead details |
| PATCH | `/api/quotations/:id/status` | 🔒 Admin | Update status |
| DELETE | `/api/quotations/:id` | 🔒 Admin | Delete lead |

#### Portfolio
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/portfolio` | Public | All albums (with ?category filter) |
| GET | `/api/portfolio/:id` | Public | Single album + images |
| POST | `/api/portfolio` | 🔒 Admin | Add album (FormData + images) |
| PATCH | `/api/portfolio/:id` | 🔒 Admin | Edit album |
| DELETE | `/api/portfolio/:id` | 🔒 Admin | Delete album |

#### Services
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/services` | Public | All services |
| POST | `/api/services` | 🔒 Admin | Add service |
| PUT | `/api/services/:id` | 🔒 Admin | Edit service |
| DELETE | `/api/services/:id` | 🔒 Admin | Delete service |

#### Clients
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/clients` | 🔒 Admin | All clients (with search) |
| POST | `/api/clients` | 🔒 Admin | Add client |
| PUT | `/api/clients/:id` | 🔒 Admin | Edit client |
| DELETE | `/api/clients/:id` | 🔒 Admin | Delete client |

#### Testimonials
| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/testimonials` | Public | Approved testimonials (for website) |
| GET | `/api/testimonials/all` | 🔒 Admin | All incl. pending |
| PATCH | `/api/testimonials/:id/approve` | 🔒 Admin | Approve |
| PATCH | `/api/testimonials/:id/reject` | 🔒 Admin | Reject |
| DELETE | `/api/testimonials/:id` | 🔒 Admin | Delete |

---

## npm Dependencies

```bash
npm install express mysql2 sequelize dotenv cors helmet morgan jsonwebtoken bcryptjs multer
```

---

## Verification Plan

### MySQL Setup (Before Starting)
1. Open XAMPP → Start **Apache** + **MySQL**
2. Go to `http://localhost/phpmyadmin`
3. Click **New** → create database: `pixcel_db`

### Automated – Run Server
```bash
cd "d:\Cinematic Admin\cinematic-backend"
node server.js
```
Expected output: `✅ Server running on port 5000` + `✅ MySQL connected`

### Manual API Tests (Postman)

| # | Test | Method | URL | Expected |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Admin Login | POST | `http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login` | `{ success: true, token: "..." }` |
| 2 | Get Quotations | GET | `http://localhost:5000/api/quotations` (with Bearer token) | Array of leads |
| 3 | Get Portfolio | GET | `http://localhost:5000/api/portfolio` | Array of albums |
| 4 | Get Services | GET | `http://localhost:5000/api/services` | Array of services |
| 5 | Get Dashboard Stats | GET | `http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/stats` (with token) | Stats object |
| 6 | Admin creds | - | email: `admin@pixcelstudio.com` / pw: `Admin@123` | Login passes |

### Frontend Connectivity Test
After backend starts, open admin panel (`npm run dev`) → Dashboard page should show real data (no hardcoded arrays).
